snippet.title: Soul Injector Commando - First 3 Levels Sample Play
snippet.description:
Work in progress. 
You can wishlist the game on Steam here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3220370/Soul_Injector_Commando/

Music by Chris Parrello
Soul Injector Commando is a game where God discovers the very people ruining Earth are the same ones she forgot to breathe souls into during a lazy period in her life. She easily finds all their names in the Forbes Real Time List of Billionaires and builds a fake underground bunker to trap them all in. You are tasked with traversing this subterranean world, to inject her breath into every single one of them, giving them souls so they can return to the world and get normal jobs like everyone else. 

Follow here or on twitter or Bluesky for updates:
https://www.twitter.com/jeremycouillard
https://bsky.app/profile/jeremycouillard.bsky.social
